OL,3,CInflatable boat crash that caused
OL,4,Cfirefighter's death an accident,
OL,5,Cinquest finds
OL,7,FThe death of a firefighter during a
OL,8,Ftraining exercise almost five years
OL,9,Fago on a river in South Wales was an
OL,10,Faccident, an inquest has found.
OL,12,FJoshua Gardener, 35, from Milford
OL,13,FHaven, Pembrokeshire, suffered a
OL,14,Fserious head injury while training
OL,15,Fwith Mid and West Wales Fire Service
OL,16,Fin September 2019.
OL,18,FThe father-of-two died when the vessel
OL,19,Fhe was on collided with another
OL,20,Finflatable craft in the Cleddau River
OL,21,Fin Pembrokeshire.
