OL,7,FThe impact threw Mr Gardener into the
OL,8,Fwater and he hit his head, causing a
OL,9,F"deep chop wound".
OL,11,FA member of the crew jumped into the
OL,12,Fwater to rescue him, but it quickly
OL,13,Fbecame apparent that Mr Gardener was
OL,14,Fdead.
OL,16,FThe crew was met at Neyland Yacht Club
OL,17,Fby ambulance and police services, and
OL,18,Fhe was pronounced dead at 11:55am.
