OL,7,FAn inquest into his death was opened
OL,8,Fat Pembrokeshire Coroner's Court in
OL,9,FHaverfordwest on Tuesday by acting
OL,10,Fsenior coroner Paul Bennett.
OL,12,FMr Bennett told the jury that a post-
OL,13,Fmortem examination found Mr Gardener
OL,14,Fdied of "disruption of the head".
OL,16,FReturning a conclusion, the jury ruled
OL,17,Fthat the incident was an accident.
