OL,7,FThe jury heard that Mr Gardener had
OL,8,Fjoined the fire service the year
OL,9,Fbefore, having been his dream to join
OL,10,Fthe emergency services since he was
OL,11,Fyoung.
OL,13,FHe had previously worked as an
OL,14,Foffshore wind farm technician.
OL,16,FA statement by his family was read
OL,17,Fout, describing Mr Gardener as a "son
OL,18,Fto be proud of" who cared deeply for
OL,19,Fhis family.
