OL,4,Cfirefighter's death an accident,
OL,5,Cinquest finds
OL,7,FThe jury was read sections of a Marine
OL,8,FAccident Investigation Branch (MAIB)
OL,9,Freport, which found there were issues
OL,10,Fin preparation on land and on the
OL,11,Fwater, and the exercise had not been
OL,12,Fplanned.
OL,14,FThe report said it was unclear why the
OL,15,Fhelmsman of one of the vessels had
OL,16,Fdecided to undertake a full circle
OL,17,Fturn, given its proximity to the other
OL,18,Fcraft and that it had been agreed they
OL,19,Fwould rendezvous further upstream
