OL,3,CInflatable boat crash that caused
OL,4,Cfirefighter's death an accident,
OL,5,Cinquest finds
OL,7,FIt said: "Neither crew was keeping an
OL,8,Feffective lookout, and so lacked
OL,9,Fawareness of the two boats' relative
OL,10,Fpositions and movements.
OL,12,F"Mid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService's pre-activity planning
OL,14,Frequirements were not met and its
OL,15,Fstandard operating procedures were not
OL,16,Ffollowed, with the consequence that:
OL,17,Fno individual had responsibility for
OL,18,Fthe overall activity; no-one was
OL,19,Fnominated to be in charge."
