OL,7,FProtective headgear was present on
OL,8,Fboth vessels but none of the crew were
OL,9,Fwearing it, with some firefighters
OL,10,Fsuggesting it was "uncomfortable to
OL,11,Fwear" and hampered communication.
OL,13,FHowever, the MAIB report said it is
OL,14,Funlikely it would have prevented Mr
OL,15,FGardener's death, had it been worn.
